      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Memories of That Day",
        "Client": "Minoto the Hub Maiden",
        "Description": "(It\u0027s actually a request from a certain\r\ntailor, but it\u0027s written by Minoto...)\r\n\u0022The reward is material for layered\r\narmor. And, uh, the armor is kind\r\nof...adorable, so...after you make it,\r\nI think I\u0027ll order another in secret...\u0022",
        "Target": "Hunt a Great Izuchi, a Mizutsune,\r\nand Magnamalo",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "En souvenir de ce jour",
        "Client": "Minoto la r\u00E9ceptionniste",
        "Description": "(Une requ\u00EAte d\u0027une certaine\r\ncouturi\u00E8re, mais \u00E9crite... par\r\nMinoto ?) \u0022Tu auras du mat\u00E9riel\r\npour une armure sp\u00E9ciale en\r\nr\u00E9compense. Et... euh... l\u0027armure est\r\nmignonne, donc... je pense en\r\ncommander une moi aussi...\u0022",
        "Target": "Chasser un Grand Izuchi, un Mizutsune\r\net le Magnamalo",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Ricordi di quel giorno",
        "Client": "Minoto la receptionist",
        "Description": "(In realt\u00E0 \u00E8 la richiesta di un\r\nsarto, ma scritta da Minoto...)\r\n\u0022Come ricompensa riceverai dei\r\nmateriali per stili armatura.\r\nEhm, l\u0027armatura \u00E8... carina\r\nquindi, dopo averla creata, ne\r\nordiner\u00F2 un\u0027altra di nascosto...\u0022",
        "Target": "Caccia un Gran Izuchi, un Mizutsune\r\ne il Magnamalo",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Erinnerungen an jenen Tag",
        "Client": "Minoto das St\u00E4tten-M\u00E4del",
        "Description": "(Bitte von einem Schneider,\r\naber geschrieben von Minoto)\r\n\u0022Die Belohnung ist Material\r\nf\u00FCr eine Dekorr\u00FCstung. Und,\r\n\u00E4h, sie ist ziemlich niedlich.\r\nWenn du es schaffst, bestelle\r\nich mir heimlich auch eine...\u0022",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Gro\u00DF-Izuchi, einen\r\nMizutsune und Magnamalo.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Recuerdos del pasado",
        "Client": "Minoto de la recepci\u00F3n",
        "Description": "(Es la petici\u00F3n de una sastre,\r\npero la ha escrito Minoto\u2026).\r\nLa recompensa es material para\r\nuna armadura superpuesta.\r\nEs una cucada de armadura,\r\nas\u00ED que creo que pedir\u00E9 una\r\npara m\u00ED cuando la hayas hecho.",
